claim.claim-text:
12. A method for classifying an activity of a user on the basis of measurements performed by a plurality of sensors comprised in a mobile device associated with said user, the method comprising:
obtaining a set of measurements from said plurality of sensors;
iteratively deriving user events from said set of measurements, said user events comprising time data, user location data, and user movement data;
analyzing said iteratively derived user events to obtain predictions regarding said user events;
analyzing said iteratively derived user events and said predictions to obtain circumstances regarding said user events, said circumstances comprising a classification of said user events as a certain activity; and
outputting said circumstances to an information system.
